Detailed Description

RTRProxyManagedObjectPoolClient is the abstract base class for application components which wish to register with one or more instances of RTRProxyManagedObjectPool in order to be notified when objects are added to or removed from a pool.

RTRProxyManagedObjectPool, RTRProxyManagedObject
